<contentList>
	<content contentuid="he29a3a37g907ag4627ga39fgd5c068e6cd0e" version="1">Origin Cloak Box</content>
	<content contentuid="h96a00b9age641g42a4g9b45gd5fc956d638b" version="1">An old wooden box smelling faintly of campfires.</content>
	<content contentuid="hf7fd6fcfg81ceg4ff6g88d5g1871a6ccc11e" version="1">Hell's Champion</content>  
	<content contentuid="hd8345163g51dfg41c1g8c4fg3172c878ff75" version="1">A hero needs a cape.</content>
	<content contentuid="h44ec0a99g84c4g4635ga9d0g0057e95d31c0" version="1">Pacted Warrior</content>  
	<content contentuid="hfd5ceb83gb96bg4d7bg80bdgc676ae5571c4" version="1">The wearer adds fire damage equal to their Charisma modifier to weapon damage rolls.</content>
	<content contentuid="h6bc13e67ga6c1g428fga1cfgdbdd32a4eb24" version="1">Mystral Cloak</content>  
	<content contentuid="h56e77a09g171dg4edcga256g5b36d5adf64d" version="1">This cloak twists in the currents of the Weave.</content>
	<content contentuid="hb4c773ccg838dg4ed8g85d3g6e23a9259055" version="1">Strands of the Weave</content>  
	<content contentuid="h6fe23effg0696g4fa9g9561ge314a9394490" version="1">Alleviate the arcane burden of spellcasting with the power of this cloak. The next spell you cast doesn't cost a &lt;LSTag Tooltip="SpellSlot"&gt;spell slot&lt;/LSTag&gt;.</content>
	<content contentuid="hb6ebdce9g8b20g4c6cga35eg91f2a05da673" version="1">Defensive Magics</content>
	<content contentuid="hfc00b82fgd201g44f6ga476gebe068968b3a" version="1">Kithraki Drape</content>  
	<content contentuid="h94b53e79g7972g42c4ga53dge58c91db042e" version="1">The red dragon riders of Tu'narath soar into battle with these cloaks whipping behind them.</content>
	<content contentuid="h0a06b69dg092bg4d7dg86abg2356df77f9d9" version="1">Shadowed Cloak</content>  
	<content contentuid="h9b2b0e51gec7ag4a89ga8bdg944145604b73" version="1">All that falls beneath this cloak is shrouded in hungry darkness.</content>
	<content contentuid="h7d5b8a3ag4b68g4188ga322g8139d71f56ac" version="1">Shadowed Words</content>  
	<content contentuid="hd10a6af4g2695g448dgb4a4g19a6d9012b21" version="1">the wearer has +[1] to spell attack rolls when they are obscured.</content>
	<content contentuid="h81f44501g5fc2g40ecg8429gb429a39a898b" version="1">Moonlit Cloak</content>  
	<content contentuid="h3c1b6405gb83cg4208ga4f4gf64a72a98373" version="1">This cloak shimmers with moonlight, keeping the darkness at bay.</content>
	<content contentuid="hf981062fg4394g4194g88d1g3c7a7d94b189" version="1">Silvered Words</content>  
	<content contentuid="ha758b58bg3be9g4302ga137gd5275c49f8c9" version="1">the wearer has +[1] to spell attack rolls when they are illuminated.</content>
	<content contentuid="hdf964a7bgf50dg4890g8169g3b99db6bce4a" version="1">Nightstalker's Shade</content>  
	<content contentuid="h11b10befg0d01g4e80g9f36ge383eb9fd7ce" version="1">A darkened drape made of membranous leather wih a black fur ruff.</content>  
	<content contentuid="he0d22705g4d52g4257gb9ddge487ea4b644b" version="1">Nightstalker</content>
	<content contentuid="h96e7682dg2fd9g46e1gb1bdgd4aebd5b4d54" version="1">The wearer has advantage on attacks while obscured.</content>
	<content contentuid="h73a7ec8cgc5fcg4863gb538g3d659418fabe" version="1">Call upon your vampiric curse to transform into a bat.</content>
	<content contentuid="ha9c4c4d1gc0c4g410bg89c4g91888850224c" version="1">Hellfire Cloak</content>
	<content contentuid="hcf0f792bg3f22g4c6dgbdefg3a219dffcfba" version="1">Smelling strongly of brimstone, this cloak was woven in the fiery heart of the Hells themselves.</content>
	<content contentuid="ha5bcb236g2846g40acg8f8fg2bdd4068430b" version="1">Embershroud</content>
	<content contentuid="hb3355effg5085g41c9gb760gb797887e5f42" version="1">Whenever a creature deals melee damage to the wearer, that creature takes [1].</content>
	<content contentuid="h6c501e3fg3ec9g4c83g8c35g5b2e7dc2efdf" version="1">Wildheart Shroud</content>
	<content contentuid="hb8038808gec6bg4f8fgab23g90631efc9293" version="1">The breeze whispers through the folds of this cloak with the sound of trees swaying upon the wind.</content>
	<content contentuid="h30ec174ag60d1g41aeg94c3g12ed82e91b27" version="1">Oakfather's Will</content>
	<content contentuid="h88c176acg2174g4aafg825fgbcfeb1937f8a" version="1">You have advantage on rolls to maintain concentration.</content>
	<content contentuid="h35dc751cg3661g4f29ga652g602559053f3c" version="1">Primal Strike</content>
	<content contentuid="h922f621ag0657g410cgac4cg8983e3b0a109" version="1">While shapeshifting or disguising itself, the wearer gains a +[1] bonus to damage rolls.</content>
	<content contentuid="ha4ee31dagbc11g4828gb55fg89ea1bc38930" version="1">Nightwarden's Mantle</content>
	<content contentuid="h8b8084c1g9b6dg419egbca7ge7ab2e752200" version="1">The nobility of menzoberranzan must ever be wary of a dagger in the dark.</content>
	<content contentuid="hd4f4a0e7g43f7g477dgbe4cg7e947c5a5205" version="1">Ever Vigilant</content>
	<content contentuid="h3dcba21dgbbf9g4469gacbdg60bc33f7ac5b" version="1">The wearer cannot be surprised.</content>
	<content contentuid="h375eda7eg1cb5g45e4gbb17g0a77ade167ac" version="1">Feet Aflame</content>
	<content contentuid="h095cedf1g629fg43fdga2d1g992c32583d00" version="1">Whenever the wearer deals Fire damage with a spell or &lt;LSTag Tooltip="Cantrip"&gt;cantrip&lt;/LSTag&gt;, they gain &lt;LSTag Type="Status" Tooltip="MAG_MOMENTUM"&gt;Momentum&lt;/LSTag&gt; for 2 turns.</content>
	<content contentuid="h713e63b6gf4b8g489cg94f9g759f262585a3" version="1">Cloak of the Protagonist</content>
	<content contentuid="h8b0931f4g41d8g4360g8a4agd32fa8c3aa67" version="1">This cloak has big main character energy.</content>
	<content contentuid="h1dad0913gdbd8g402bgac3cg8fa5219e6999" version="1">Defy Death</content>
	<content contentuid="hc57d5037g9b69g4089ga8b1gcb1d7563bf92" version="1">The wearer of this cloak has advantage on death saving throws.</content>
	<content contentuid="hfde5e27age910g4127gb6b3gdfad310f68c8" version="1">Beat the Odds</content>
</contentList>

